				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$[0,t_\text{fit}]$$\end{document}[0,tfit] and second to allow one (in deterministic mode) or repeated runs (in stochastic mode) on the interval \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
