				\begin{document}$$[t_\text{fit},t_\text{fin}]$$\end{document}[tfit,tfin]. The latter can be either executed by incorporating demographic stochasticity alone, or it can include a file of parameter values obtained from an MCMC fit of the model to data.Fig. 4
